title: Grateful Dead Live at The Greek Theatre - University Of California on 1989-08-18
venue: The Greek Theatre - University Of California
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.6MHz) > Tascam Hi-Res Editor (WAV 24-bit/96k) > Adobe Audition CC 2022 > Samplitude Pro X6 Suite > FLAC/24
taper: Recorded by Don Pearson and Dan Healy
description:
Set I
Cold Rain & Snow
New Minglewood Blues
Row Jimmy
When I Paint My Masterpiece
Built To Last
Victim Or The Crime >
Bird Song
Promised Land
Set II
Iko Iko

Drums >
Space >
Crazy Fingers >
I Need A Miracle >

Throwing Stones >
Turn On Your Lovelight

Encore:
Black Muddy River
We Bid You Good Night

Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
